title: Al Roker to headline Weather Channel's digital show - WKXW-FM Trenton
text:
In this March 16, 2015 file photo, Al Roker attends the premiere of "The Divergent Series: Insurgent" at the Ziegfeld Theatre in New York. He's the headliner for "The Lift," a digital offering that could have intriguing implications for television programs.
 WKXW-FM Trenton.
